cab.content: BATTLE SITUATION - EVENING - 14th MAY., 1918.1. Australian troops carried out a successful raidlast night in tho neighbourhood of MORIANCOURT, and captured 43 prisoners.2. Thoro is nothing of special interest to report onthe rest of the front and no change in the general situation.General Staff,War Office, S,W.l. 14th May, 1918.Issued at G,0 p.m.
